<ext_description linkend="Product_class_mim.characterized_product_concept_feature">
  A <b>characterized_product_concept_feature</b> is a type of 
  <express_ref linkend="product_concept_schema:ir_express:product_concept_schema.product_concept_feature"/>
  and of
  <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.characterized_object"/>
  that allows a
  <express_ref linkend="product_concept_schema:ir_express:product_concept_schema.product_concept_feature"/>
  to be characterized.
  A <b>characterized_product_concept_feature</b> implements the ARM concept of a
  <express_ref linkend="product_class:arm:Product_class_arm.Specification"/>
  that may be referenced by an 
  <express_ref linkend="property_assignment:arm:Property_assignment_arm.Assigned_property"/>
  through the attribute
  <express_ref linkend="property_assignment:arm:Property_assignment_arm.Assigned_property.described_element"/>.
</ext_description>


<ext_description linkend="Product_class_mim.characterized_product_concept_feature_category">
  A <b>characterized_product_concept_feature_category</b> is a type of 
  <express_ref linkend="product_class:mim:Product_class_mim.product_concept_feature_category"/>
  and of
  <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.characterized_object"/>
  that allows a
  <express_ref linkend="product_class:mim:Product_class_mim.product_concept_feature_category"/>
  to be characterized.
  A <b>characterized_product_concept_feature_category</b> implements the ARM concept of a
  <express_ref linkend="product_class:arm:Product_class_arm.Specification_category"/>
  that may be referenced by an 
  <express_ref linkend="property_assignment:arm:Property_assignment_arm.Assigned_property"/>
  through the attribute
  <express_ref linkend="property_assignment:arm:Property_assignment_arm.Assigned_property.described_element"/>.
</ext_description>


	<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Product_class_mim  Entity: exclusive_product_concept_feature_category  
   <express_ref linkend="product_class:mim:Product_class_mim.exclusive_product_concept_feature_category"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
	<ext_description linkend="Product_class_mim.exclusive_product_concept_feature_category">
An <b>exclusive_product_concept_feature_category</b> is a type of <express_ref linkend="product_class:mim:Product_class_mim.product_concept_feature_category"/> the members of which describe mutually exclusive characteristics of a product.
</ext_description>
	<!-- 

  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Product_class_mim  Entity: inclusion_product_concept_feature  
   <express_ref linkend="product_class:mim:Product_class_mim.inclusion_product_concept_feature"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
	<ext_description linkend="Product_class_mim.inclusion_product_concept_feature">
An <b>inclusion_product_concept_feature</b> is a type of <express_ref linkend="product_concept_schema:ir_express:product_concept_schema.conditional_concept_feature"/> that represents the statement that the application of a <express_ref linkend="product_concept_schema:ir_express:product_concept_schema.product_concept_feature"/> or of a <express_ref linkend="product_concept_schema:ir_express:product_concept_schema.conditional_concept_feature"/> involves the inclusion of an additional <express_ref linkend="product_concept_schema:ir_express:product_concept_schema.product_concept_feature"/> or <express_ref linkend="product_concept_schema:ir_express:product_concept_schema.conditional_concept_feature"/>.

</ext_description>
	<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Product_class_mim  Entity: inclusion_product_concept_feature  Where: wr1 
   <express_ref linkend="product_class:mim:Product_class_mim.inclusion_product_concept_feature.wr:wr1"/>

  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
	<ext_description linkend="Product_class_mim.inclusion_product_concept_feature.wr:WR1">
an <b>inclusion_product_concept_feature</b> shall not be of type <express_ref linkend="product_class:mim:Product_class_mim.package_product_concept_feature"/>. 
</ext_description>
	<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Product_class_mim  Entity: inclusion_product_concept_feature  Where: wr2 
   <express_ref linkend="product_class:mim:Product_class_mim.inclusion_product_concept_feature.wr:wr2"/>

  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
	<ext_description linkend="Product_class_mim.inclusion_product_concept_feature.wr:WR2">
an <b>inclusion_product_concept_feature</b> shall not be referenced as <express_ref linkend="product_concept_schema:ir_express:product_concept_schema.concept_feature_relationship.relating_product_concept_feature"/> nor as <express_ref linkend="product_concept_schema:ir_express:product_concept_schema.concept_feature_relationship.related_product_concept_feature"/> by <express_ref linkend="product_concept_schema:ir_express:product_concept_schema.concept_feature_relationship_with_condition"/> instances.

</ext_description>
	<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Product_class_mim  Entity: inclusion_product_concept_feature  Where: wr3 
   <express_ref linkend="product_class:mim:Product_class_mim.inclusion_product_concept_feature.wr:wr3"/>

  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
	<ext_description linkend="Product_class_mim.inclusion_product_concept_feature.wr:WR3">
an <b>inclusion_product_concept_feature</b> shall reference as condition a <express_ref linkend="product_concept_schema:ir_express:product_concept_schema.concept_feature_relationship_with_condition"/> which references a <express_ref linkend="product_concept_schema:ir_express:product_concept_schema.concept_feature_operator"/> with a name of 'implication'.

</ext_description>
	<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Product_class_mim  Entity: package_product_concept_feature  
   <express_ref linkend="product_class:mim:Product_class_mim.package_product_concept_feature"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
	<ext_description linkend="Product_class_mim.package_product_concept_feature">
A <b>package_product_concept_feature</b> is a type of <express_ref linkend="product_concept_schema:ir_express:product_concept_schema.product_concept_feature"/> that is a collection of product features that shall be offered to the market as a set.
The content of the package shall be described with an instance of <express_ref linkend="product_class:mim:Product_class_mim.inclusion_product_concept_feature"/>.

</ext_description>
	<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Product_class_mim  Entity: package_product_concept_feature  Where: wr1 
   <express_ref linkend="product_class:mim:Product_class_mim.package_product_concept_feature.wr:wr1"/>

  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
	<ext_description linkend="Product_class_mim.package_product_concept_feature.wr:WR1">
a <b>package_product_concept_feature</b> shall not be of type <express_ref linkend="product_concept_schema:ir_express:product_concept_schema.conditional_concept_feature"/>. 
</ext_description>
	<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Product_class_mim  Entity: package_product_concept_feature  Where: wr2 
   <express_ref linkend="product_class:mim:Product_class_mim.package_product_concept_feature.wr:wr2"/>

  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
	<ext_description linkend="Product_class_mim.package_product_concept_feature.wr:WR2">

a <b>package_product_concept_feature</b> shall be referenced as <express_ref linkend="product_concept_schema:ir_express:product_concept_schema.concept_feature_relationship.relating_product_concept_feature"/> by at least one <express_ref linkend="product_concept_schema:ir_express:product_concept_schema.concept_feature_relationship_with_condition"/> which is referenced as condition by a <express_ref linkend="product_concept_schema:ir_express:product_concept_schema.conditional_concept_feature"/> of type <express_ref linkend="product_class:mim:Product_class_mim.inclusion_product_concept_feature"/>. 

</ext_description>
	<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Product_class_mim  Entity: product_class  
   <express_ref linkend="product_class:mim:Product_class_mim.product_class"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
	<ext_description linkend="Product_class_mim.product_class">
A <b>product_class</b> is a type of <express_ref linkend="product_concept_schema:ir_express:product_concept_schema.product_concept"/> and of <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.characterized_object"/> that is the identification of a set of similar products to be offered to the market.
<note>The fact that the <b>product_class</b> entity is a subtype of the <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.characterized_object"/> entity enables to assign properties to characterize the product class.
</note>
	</ext_description>
	<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Product_class_mim  Entity: product_concept_feature_category  
   <express_ref linkend="product_class:mim:Product_class_mim.product_concept_feature_category"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
	<ext_description linkend="Product_class_mim.product_concept_feature_category">
A <b>product_concept_feature_category</b> is a type of <express_ref linkend="group_schema:ir_express:group_schema.group"/> that identifies a set of similar product features represented with <express_ref linkend="product_concept_schema:ir_express:product_concept_schema.product_concept_feature"/> instances.
<example>The body color for cars or the kind of wood for pieces of furniture are examples of <b>product_concept_feature_category</b>.
</example>
	</ext_description>
	<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Product_class_mim  Entity: product_concept_feature_category  Where: WR1 
   <express_ref linkend="product_class:mim:Product_class_mim.product_concept_feature_category.wr:WR1"/>

  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
	<ext_description linkend="Product_class_mim.product_concept_feature_category.wr:WR1">
		<p>
a <b>product_concept_feature_category</b> shall only be referenced as <express_ref linkend="management_resources_schema:ir_express:management_resources_schema.group_assignment.assigned_group"/> by <express_ref linkend="group:mim:Group_mim.applied_group_assignment"/> instances:
</p>
		<ul>
			<li>which reference as <express_ref linkend="management_resources_schema:ir_express:management_resources_schema.group_assignment.role"/> an <express_ref linkend="basic_attribute_schema:ir_express:basic_attribute_schema.object_role"/> with a name of 'specification category member', and</li>
			<li>which only contain in their set of items instances of <express_ref linkend="product_concept_schema:ir_express:product_concept_schema.product_concept_feature"/> that are not of type <express_ref linkend="product_concept_schema:ir_express:product_concept_schema.conditional_concept_feature"/>. </li>
		</ul>
	</ext_description>
	<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Product_class_mim  Entity: product_concept_feature_category_usage  
   <express_ref linkend="product_class:mim:Product_class_mim.product_concept_feature_category_usage"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
	<ext_description linkend="Product_class_mim.product_concept_feature_category_usage">
A <b>product_concept_feature_category_usage</b> is a type of <express_ref linkend="management_resources_schema:ir_express:management_resources_schema.group_assignment"/> that associates a <express_ref linkend="product_class:mim:Product_class_mim.product_concept_feature_category"/> with one or more instances of <express_ref linkend="product_class:mim:Product_class_mim.product_class"/>, referred to by the inherited attribute items. 
<p>Additionally, this assignment specifies if the usage of one or more product features belonging to this <express_ref linkend="product_class:mim:Product_class_mim.product_concept_feature_category"/> is mandatory or optional for all products of the product classes.
</p>
	</ext_description>
	<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Product_class_mim  Entity: product_concept_feature_category_usage  Attribute: assigned_group 
   <express_ref linkend="product_class:mim:Product_class_mim.product_concept_feature_category_usage.assigned_group"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
	<ext_description linkend="Product_class_mim.product_concept_feature_category_usage.assigned_group">
the <express_ref linkend="product_class:mim:Product_class_mim.product_concept_feature_category"/> that is considered.
</ext_description>
	<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Product_class_mim  Entity: product_concept_feature_category_usage  Attribute: items 
   <express_ref linkend="product_class:mim:Product_class_mim.product_concept_feature_category_usage.items"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
	<ext_description linkend="Product_class_mim.product_concept_feature_category_usage.items">
the set of instances of types listed in <express_ref linkend="product_class:mim:Product_class_mim.category_usage_item"/> to which the <express_ref linkend="product_class:mim:Product_class_mim.product_concept_feature_category"/> is assigned.

</ext_description>
	<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Product_class_mim  Entity: product_concept_feature_category_usage  Where: WR1 
   <express_ref linkend="product_class:mim:Product_class_mim.product_concept_feature_category_usage.wr:WR1"/>

  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
	<ext_description linkend="Product_class_mim.product_concept_feature_category_usage.wr:WR1">
the <b>product_concept_feature_category_usage</b> shall have as <express_ref linkend="management_resources_schema:ir_express:management_resources_schema.group_assignment.role"/> an <express_ref linkend="basic_attribute_schema:ir_express:basic_attribute_schema.object_role"/> with a name of 'mandatory category usage' or 'optional category usage'. 
</ext_description>
	<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Product_class_mim  Rule: restrict_concept_feature_operator 
   <express_ref linkend="product_class:mim:Product_class_mim.restrict_concept_feature_operator"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
	<ext_description linkend="Product_class_mim.restrict_concept_feature_operator">
The <b>restrict_concept_feature_operator</b> rule restricts the name and usage of a <express_ref linkend="product_concept_schema:ir_express:product_concept_schema.concept_feature_operator"/>. 
</ext_description>
	<ext_description linkend="Product_class_mim.restrict_concept_feature_operator.wr:WR1">
each instance of <express_ref linkend="product_concept_schema:ir_express:product_concept_schema.concept_feature_operator"/> shall have a name of 'and', 'or', 'oneof, 'not', or 'implication'. 
</ext_description>
	<ext_description linkend="Product_class_mim.restrict_concept_feature_operator.wr:WR2">
if a <express_ref linkend="product_concept_schema:ir_express:product_concept_schema.concept_feature_operator"/> has a name of 'implication', it shall only be referenced as <express_ref linkend="product_concept_schema:ir_express:product_concept_schema.concept_feature_relationship_with_condition.conditional_operator"/> by <express_ref linkend="product_concept_schema:ir_express:product_concept_schema.concept_feature_relationship_with_condition"/> instances which are referenced as the condition by <express_ref linkend="product_concept_schema:ir_express:product_concept_schema.conditional_concept_feature"/> instances which are of type <express_ref linkend="product_class:mim:Product_class_mim.inclusion_product_concept_feature"/>. 
</ext_description>
	<ext_description linkend="Product_class_mim.restrict_concept_feature_operator.wr:WR3">
if a <express_ref linkend="product_concept_schema:ir_express:product_concept_schema.concept_feature_operator"/> has a name of 'not', it shall only be referenced as <express_ref linkend="product_concept_schema:ir_express:product_concept_schema.concept_feature_relationship_with_condition.conditional_operator"/> by <express_ref linkend="product_concept_schema:ir_express:product_concept_schema.concept_feature_relationship_with_condition"/> instances where the attribute <express_ref linkend="product_concept_schema:ir_express:product_concept_schema.concept_feature_relationship.relating_product_concept_feature"/> refers to the same instance as the attribute <express_ref linkend="product_concept_schema:ir_express:product_concept_schema.concept_feature_relationship.related_product_concept_feature"/>. 

</ext_description>
	<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Product_class_mim  Rule: restrict_group_relationship_for_specification_category 
   <express_ref linkend="product_class:mim:Product_class_mim.restrict_group_relationship_for_specification_category"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
	<ext_description linkend="Product_class_mim.restrict_group_relationship_for_specification_category">
The <b>restrict_group_relationship_for_specification_category</b> rule ensures the correct correlation between the name of a <express_ref linkend="group_schema:ir_express:group_schema.group_relationship"/> and the type of the related groups. 
</ext_description>
	<ext_description linkend="Product_class_mim.restrict_group_relationship_for_specification_category.wr:WR1">
if a <express_ref linkend="group_schema:ir_express:group_schema.group_relationship"/> has a name of 'specification category hierarchy', the <express_ref linkend="group_schema:ir_express:group_schema.group_relationship.related_group"/> and the <express_ref linkend="group_schema:ir_express:group_schema.group_relationship.relating_group"/> shall be of type <express_ref linkend="product_class:mim:Product_class_mim.product_concept_feature_category"/>.
</ext_description>
	<!-- 
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
   Schema: Product_class_mim  Rule: product_concept_feature_requires_category 
   <express_ref linkend="product_class:mim:Product_class_mim.product_concept_feature_requires_category"/>
  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->
	<ext_description linkend="Product_class_mim.product_concept_feature_requires_category">
The <b>product_concept_feature_requires_category</b> rule specifies that each instance of <express_ref linkend="product_concept_schema:ir_express:product_concept_schema.product_concept_feature"/> that is not an <express_ref linkend="product_class:mim:Product_class_mim.inclusion_product_concept_feature"/> nor a <express_ref linkend="product_concept_schema:ir_express:product_concept_schema.conditional_concept_feature"/>, 
is a member of exactly one <express_ref linkend="product_class:mim:Product_class_mim.product_concept_feature_category"/>. This membership is represented by the fact that the <express_ref linkend="product_concept_schema:ir_express:product_concept_schema.product_concept_feature"/> is contained in the set of items of exactly one <express_ref linkend="group:mim:Group_mim.applied_group_assignment"/> which has, as the <express_ref linkend="management_resources_schema:ir_express:management_resources_schema.group_assignment.role"/>, an <express_ref linkend="basic_attribute_schema:ir_express:basic_attribute_schema.object_role"/> with name 'specification category member' and which references, as the <express_ref linkend="management_resources_schema:ir_express:management_resources_schema.group_assignment.assigned_group"/>, a <express_ref linkend="product_class:mim:Product_class_mim.product_concept_feature_category"/>. 
</ext_description>
	<ext_description linkend="Product_class_mim.product_concept_feature_requires_category.wr:WR1">
each instance of <express_ref linkend="product_concept_schema:ir_express:product_concept_schema.product_concept_feature"/> is contained in the set of items of exactly one <express_ref linkend="group:mim:Group_mim.applied_group_assignment"/> which has as the <express_ref linkend="management_resources_schema:ir_express:management_resources_schema.group_assignment.role"/> an <express_ref linkend="basic_attribute_schema:ir_express:basic_attribute_schema.object_role"/> with name 'specification category member' and which references as the <express_ref linkend="management_resources_schema:ir_express:management_resources_schema.group_assignment.assigned_group"/> a <express_ref linkend="product_class:mim:Product_class_mim.product_concept_feature_category"/>.

</ext_description>
</ext_descriptions>
